title: Quick Take: April 26 Primary Results
description: A wrap of results from Tuesday's contests, when Hillary Clinton and Donald Trump won in Connecticut, Delaware, Maryland, and Pennsylvania — with Bernie Sanders taking Rhode Island.  This episode: host/campaign reporter Sam Sanders and editor/correspondent Ron Elving. More coverage at nprpolitics.org. Email the show at nprpolitics@npr.org.
